metadata.name: Opposition
metadata.description:
Confrontations between the people and the police during the G20 London Summit protests.  That day Ian Tomlinson died after being assaulted by police while trying to make his way home. 

Do you want to donate to Inquest?  
Every year INQUEST supports hundreds of families bereaved by state related deaths. Alongside those families, we help drive systemic change to prevent future deaths.  
www.inquest.org.uk/appeal/make-donation

Artist: Alex Bartsch

Edition of 30
